=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 40.25%; height: 21.5px; border-top:none;border-right:1px dashed rgb(210, 210, 210);border-left:none;border-bottom:1px dashed rgb(210, 210, 210); background-color: #e3fdc8;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-39dadc07-be14-40ab-b172-438fa8cf8239\" style=\"line-height:1.6;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-61da4115-1d6b-414d-8c36-89f5b7867c54\" style=\"color:#333333;\"><b>카탈로그</b></span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 44.88%; height: 21.5px; border-top:none;border-right:1px dashed rgb(210, 210, 210);border-left:none;border-bottom:1px dashed rgb(210, 210, 210); background-color: #e3fdc8;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-372c50b0-44f9-4b07-a998-351eb6a6d3ca\" style=\"line-height:1.6;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9c8f48c7-48b8-4dfa-9037-591f2beb7ccd\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>지명원</b></span></p></div>\n</td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 14.87%; height: 36.17px; border-top:none;border-right:1px dashed rgb(210, 210, 210);border-left:none;border-bottom:1px dashed rgb(210, 210, 210); background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0efed763-952e-4547-a95a-a157ed29a1c9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-7cda3a56-f2bb-446e-b273-72b50d62cee6\" style=\"\"><b>개요</b></span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 40.25%; height: -82.25px; border-top:none;border-right:1px dashed rgb(210, 210, 210);border-left:none;border-bottom:1px dashed rgb(210, 210, 210); \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5ab666ef-654e-4afe-b4fd-43b89e0ea453\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-ef21b8ef-9f9c-4feb-ba91-97041e82d70d\" style=\"\"><b>회사 홍보를 목적으로 만드는 인쇄물입니다. 보통 제품 카탈로그처럼 회사의 생산품이나 서비스를 주요 내용으로 담습니다.</b></span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 44.88%; height: -82.25px; border-top:none;border-right:1px dashed rgb(210, 210, 210);border-left:none;border-bottom:1px dashed rgb(210, 210, 210); \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fbd8b98b-4e8f-4091-ac80-b72a1a357606\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-f8443749-99ae-4c56-bb70-d21f17cc7e36\" style=\"\"><b>입찰이나 견적을 제출하기 위해 회사의 실적이나 자산 위주로 만든 인쇄물입니다. 지명원에는 보유 자격증, 특허, 실적, 재무 등을 주요 내용으로 담고 있습니다.</b></span></p></div>\n</td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 14.87%; height: 18.09px; border-top:none;border-right:1px dashed rgb(210, 210, 210);border-left:none;border-bottom:1px dashed rgb(210, 210, 210); background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8481ade7-21af-4840-9800-0778f93486b3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-a19d2c8e-8cd7-40cc-84e0-0407c26c5fbc\" style=\"\"><b>주요 내용</b></span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 40.25%; height: -41.13px; border-top:none;border-right:1px dashed rgb(210, 210, 210);border-left:none;border-bottom:1px dashed rgb(210, 210, 210); \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bacb96e7-9f5c-4989-b75f-0a7d9f7a2e7a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-92e3c773-17e5-40f0-bf54-3ac4491814ed\" style=\"\">회사소개</span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragrap