><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 40.25%; height: -20.56px; border-top:none;border-right:1px dashed rgb(210, 210, 210);border-left:none;border-bottom:1px dashed rgb(210, 210, 210); \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bb6a413e-e836-4370-aa9d-f4ed4ef2e78d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-a848e9b6-8d58-4ca5-bece-0c2d5b6bccc3\" style=\"\">디자인 강조</span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8003bded-1df3-4c97-9504-f761bda08b45\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-fd7fcdca-325c-42bf-aded-803334bb0477\" style=\"\">홍보 목적</span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a6717f75-d442-49a5-aa53-d96affd22ce7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-d01a0e0e-b405-43f4-b75b-2fb24ec40299\" style=\"\">구성이나 형식이 중요</span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 44.88%; height: -20.56px; border-top:none;border-right:1px dashed rgb(210, 210, 210);border-left:none;border-bottom:1px dashed rgb(210, 210, 210); \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3da58a09-ed35-483c-bd0e-ee2c1e544c0d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-743d2100-ba01-4a5d-937c-5248ca03d921\" style=\"\">실제 내용의 정확도</span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-98135b48-f38c-4b8a-b8af-09367870f786\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-00ec2be1-f77b-40f0-ae64-d12777b8f48f\" style=\"\">자료 제출용</span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9cfe747c-e846-4b53-ba2f-6e901251d30f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-baecf639-929a-4b42-b79b-4dc3d852b6c2\" style=\"\">프레젠테이션 발표</span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-86bac656-f919-4a28-b86b-e8f6db155e2f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-ebfd233f-7bc2-41cc-aad9-3ea2cb60d20f\" style=\"\">형식보다는 실질이 중요</span></p></div>\n</td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 14.87%; height: 9.040000000000003px; border-top:none;border-right:1px dashed rgb(210, 210, 210);border-left:none;border-bottom:1px dashed rgb(210, 210, 210); background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-341475e9-1b49-4bdd-afae-19f1901fd3cd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-b8b23075-bc86-4aa8-a4cb-22b8e6551acf\" style=\"\"><b>주의점</b></span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 40.25%; height: -20.56px; border-top:none;border-right:1px dashed rgb(210, 210, 210);border-left:none;border-bottom:1px dashed rgb(210, 210, 210); \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f51dcee3-f56c-4c76-a700-062113d78c53\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-2f06e70e-9125-469c-8863-d5f17edbabed\" style=\"\">너무 형식에 치우쳐 자칫하면 실질적인 내용이 허술하면 안 됩니다.</span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-05a189b2-fcd8-4b41-a119-95477843415e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-d3961eea-03f8-4c28-a34c-9ffd6da97220\" style=\"\">총합적으로 방대한 디자인으로 제작도 가능합니다. 다만 너무 방대할 경우 오히려 무거워질 수 있습니다.</span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 44.88%; height: -20.56px; border-top:none;border-right:1px dashed rgb(210, 210, 210);border-left:none;border-bottom:1px dashed rgb(210, 210, 210); \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3d1031c9-8297-41f5-9a61-2becb22a2d5e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-47c37bed-34bf-4834-85af-022a0e14ebba\" style=\"\">기본에 충실하지만 그렇다고 형식을 무시하면 안 됩니다.</span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f18c86b0-fbba-4346-b470-6e88a5f6e66c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-d5da3923-dfc5-40a5-aa65-3778e78c062b\" style=\"\">프레젠테이션용이라면 제작 형식이 완전히 달라집니다. 이때는 ppt 전문가와 상의해야 합니다.</span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cd55b3cd-9d12-4079-92ac-b22bec666b19\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-01bce2f7-86ef-4e1e-804e-598e8d780633\" style=\"\">ppt는 제출용과 발표용이 따로 있습니다.</span></p></div>\n</td></tr></tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5eb8ffac-7e0c-40f0-8b0a-05b50e1e6471\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:473px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link-use se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223037726792/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-da69ac12-afd2-4f6e-87e6-7db845705d8e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:473px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-im